      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p><em>Voidforged</em> is an <em>Ironsworn: Starforged</em> unofficial supplement to add a horror flavor to your sci-fi adventure.</p><p>Included are:</p><ul><li><p>Oracles</p></li><li><p>Journal entry with Truths</p></li><li><p>A One-shot Adventure</p></li></ul><p>Voidforged by Kerys can be found <a href=\"https://kerys.itch.io/voidforged\">here</a>.</p><p>Other works by Kerys can be found <a href=\"https://kerys.itch.io/\">here</a>.</p><p>This work adapts some mechanics from the Mothership Sci-Fi Horror RPG (found at <span class=\"s1\">https://www.mothershiprpg.com/home</span>), created by Tuesday Knight Games.</p><p>This work also contains conversion notes for the Mothership Sci-Fi Horror RPG.</p><ul><li><a href=\"https://kerys.itch.io/voidforged\">Voidforged</a> by <a href=\"https://kerys.itch.io/\">Kerys</a> is licensed for use under the <a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/\">Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License (CC BY)</a>.</li></ul>"
